{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_kichi_set_1", "eventName": "好運相伴", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "好運相伴", "storyInfo": "遭人設局的吉星即將被迫離開鍛冶町，離別前她逐一拜訪了鄰居們。但還沒等她啟程，設局的黑道卻先被人找了麻煩。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g15_higashiroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不大的房間裡，擺滿了一排排的小鋼珠機，而房間深處傳來一陣陣按鍵音和遊戲裡的爆炸聲。"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來新客人啦？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小鋼珠機都開著呢，投幣就能玩。飲料和零食都到櫃台自取——", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你就是吉星？", "name": "冷靜的黑道成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，不是來打小鋼珠的？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#4$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們聽說你這邊能接點別的生意，想請你幫個忙。", "name": "冷靜的黑道成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，我能接什麼別的生意，你們是不是找錯人啦……", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#5$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們老大從薩爾貢新進了一批寶石，想請你過去看看……事成以後，這個數。", "name": "冷靜的黑道成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑道成員伸出手，比了一個數字。"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（吞口水）這個數……？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "千真萬確。", "name": "冷靜的黑道成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g6_gokudouoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吉星小姐，歡迎。", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們山川會剛來御機不久，現在迫切需要一位本地人為我們開拓市場。", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好啦好啦，這些客套話都不用說了，東西在哪裡？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑道老大揮揮手，一個沉甸甸的皮箱便出現在了兩人面前的桌上。"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_open_woodbox"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼多……？！", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#6$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些都是從我一位朋友那裡收來的天然寶石，它們的大小和品質放眼全東國都是最頂級的。", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我花了不少錢才把它們收進囊中，但現在怎麼處理它們反倒成了難題……", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼多奇珍異寶在短時間內流進市場，除了會貶損它們的價值，還會引起有心之人的注意。", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽聞吉星小姐擅長鑑定珠寶，而且在御機城人脈頗廣，一定能為我找個好買家，賣個好價錢。", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等、等等！我還沒說要接你的單呢。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吉星隨手從箱子裡抓了一顆紅色的寶石，將寶石對準屋頂的射燈，端詳了許久。"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "乍看之下倒是不錯，可惜……", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……可惜？", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩爾貢的寶石雖然品質高級，但他們那邊大多都是小工坊手工製作，一年的產量少得可憐。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的這一批貨，乍看之下品種不少，但加工方式太相似了。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "切面太規則，工具都沒有換過，說明做這批貨的人經驗還比較淺。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有這裡的邊角也是，痕跡太新了，好一點的情況是出廠年份比較近，壞一點的情況……可能原料都不是天然的。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#4$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不可能……絕對不可能！", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些都是我看著他們從拍賣行的倉庫裡一件件拿出來，我一件件挑好的。", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，如果你還是不信的話……那就看這顆。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#4$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在法爾賈萬達巴德博物館裡，有一顆和它一模一樣的藍寶石，名字叫“璀璨之淚”，上面同樣嵌了一顆淚形黃金。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩爾貢的國寶，可能經過正規的拍賣行，流落到你我的手裡嗎？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……話不用我再多說了吧？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的意思是，我的這些寶貝……都是假的？", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "假的，你換誰鑑定都是假的。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……但這些寶貝都經過了專家認證。", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼……？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些寶貝都是一位議員大人轉手給我的，他的大名在東國收藏界無人不知。", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說的是藤堂——", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#6$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不能說。", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位大人把這些珠寶交給我之前，特地把它們送去了鑑定機構，這些都是專家給出的鑑定結果。", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑道老大將一本厚重的文件放在茶几上，上面印滿了各種機構的標誌。"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）*東國粗口*，這上面可沒一個惹得起啊……", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如你所見，沒有一個專家說我的寶貝是假的，除了你，吉星小姐。", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……既然已經找過了更權威的機構，幹嘛還要找我？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在一開始我就和你明說了，吉星小姐，我希望你能幫我找到一些好的買家。", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經事先找人瞭解過了，你的奶奶在御機的珠寶界久負盛名，而你接手了她的事業。", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有你的幫忙，這批貨不難出手。至於酬勞，你放心，只多不少。", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈……你在說笑呢，我就是一個替人看小鋼珠店的小妹，哪有那麼大能耐？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你還是覺得我的貨假，不想幫我。", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪有的事？我可從來沒有說過你的寶貝假哦！", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#5$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（揮揮手）", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，老大，我已經全部錄下來了。", "name": "冷靜的黑道成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你算計我？！", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#6$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是誠信交易的基本操作而已。", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吉星小姐，我完全信任你的能力。", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從議員那裡收過來這些貨，幾乎花掉了全部的家當。如果你判斷這些東西都是假的，我會拿著你的報告去跟他算帳……", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果這批貨沒有問題……你就必須幫我把這批價值幾億的珠寶全部賣出去。", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g4_kajistreet_dusk", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道吉星去哪裡了嗎？", "name": "疑惑的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小鋼珠店今天一直沒開門，門口也沒有貼通知……", "name": "疑惑的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1911_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "應該是突然有什麼事吧？這孩子很忙的啦。", "name": "不解的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1911_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，可惜今天不能玩便宜的小鋼珠了。習慣她家的價格以後，都不願意去其他家了……", "name": "疑惑的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吉星，你回來啦？！", "name": "疑惑的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚……", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1911_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼垂頭喪氣的，遇到什麼事情了？", "name": "不解的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1911_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……都怪我沒什麼戒心，早知道就不碰這種事了！", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰知道會碰到這種不能惹的人……現在要嘛幫別人賣價值幾億的假貨，要嘛倒欠人家幾億！", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#8$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1911_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾、幾億？！", "name": "疑惑的居民&不解的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#8$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把我的小店……不，把我整個人賣了都值不了這麼多錢啊！", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#8$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吉星敲著自己的腦袋，搖搖晃晃地朝自家小店走去，只留下驚詫的路人。"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夜色將近，小店的“吉星”招牌不規則地閃著，即使下一秒突然熄滅也不奇怪。"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吉星，吉星……你怎麼這麼倒楣啊？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#8$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g6_gokudouoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老大，她回家了。", "name": "冷靜的黑道成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她有什麼動作？", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有……就是抱著抱枕哭了一陣，然後在地板上不停打滾，現在在打電子遊戲。", "name": "冷靜的黑道成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……她沒有跟誰打電話？", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有。", "name": "冷靜的黑道成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老大，我們會不會盯錯目標了。她家裡除了遊戲機什麼都沒有，看著也不像是有錢人……", "name": "冷靜的黑道成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不可能！", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她奶奶當年靠賣假珠寶賺了那麼多錢，怎麼可能不留一點給她的孫女？", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前踩點的時候，她就是現在這副三天打鱗兩天曬網的樣子，說明這傢伙根本不缺錢。", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種到嘴邊的肉，我怎麼可能讓給別人？", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$phone"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 5.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂……什麼？", "name": "冷靜的黑道成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……好，我知道了。", "name": "冷靜的黑道成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老大，眼線說，她正在收拾東西！", "name": "冷靜的黑道成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，我就知道……盯緊點，別讓她跑了。", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g5_kajistreet_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "", "name": "？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "日用品、飾品、小零食，所有商品通通五折——", "name": "熱情的攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喲，吉星，你怎麼背著這麼大一個袋子？", "name": "熱情的攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鈴木大叔，我是來道別的。我可能……得離開鍛冶町一段時間了。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#9$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？發生什麼事了，怎麼突然就要離開？", "name": "鈴木大叔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒、沒發生什麼，就是……就是工作原因，我以後就不在這裡做了。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼工作這麼急……吉星，你不會是遇到什麼麻煩了吧？", "name": "鈴木大叔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有什麼事就直說，我們都是多少年的街坊鄰居了，能幫一定幫你。", "name": "鈴木大叔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（東張西望）怎麼說呢……的確是個不小的麻煩，但這些都該是我一個人承擔的，我也不想把大家都拖下水。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之……事情就是這樣。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小吉星，我真的很難過……", "name": "傷心的攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你奶奶生前對我那麼好，我也一直把你當成我的親妹妹，你怎麼說走就走了呢？", "name": "傷心的攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有你的小店該怎麼辦……？", "name": "傷心的攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小鋼珠店是鐵齋老爺子的，他肯定能找到下一個看店的人。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個店面的位置很好，即使我的店在二樓也不怕租不出去，之後說不定會開個影音商店或者拉麵店……", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#2$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（抽泣）小吉星，你不要再說了……我不想任何人在這裡開新店，我只想要你能一直在鍛冶町。", "name": "傷心的攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可、可是……姐姐，我必須得走了。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#9$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼就突然要走了呢？我聯絡一下大家，至少為你辦一個歡送會再走吧？", "name": "生氣的攤主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（東張西望）不、不用了！我明天就要走了，就不勞煩各位鄰居了。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#10$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "冷靜的黑道成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g6_gokudouoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吉星今天一整天都在外面走訪，挨家挨戶地和附近的居民道別。", "name": "冷靜的黑道成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她從一開始就注意到了我，所以鑑定和欠債的事也沒有洩露。", "name": "冷靜的黑道成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，我料定她耍不了花招。", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說不定……她是在為自己後面借錢做準備。", "name": "冷靜的黑道成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一條破街上的小商小販，能有多大能耐？", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我倒要看看她究竟能躲到什麼時候……", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g10_higashigarden_r", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……今天不打牌了，沒心情打。", "name": "？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吉星的事，你們都知道了？", "name": "？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小女生一大早就跑過來告別，一臉苦兮兮的，誰看到不心疼……", "name": "？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "查得到後面是誰？", "name": "？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這兩天街上有幾個生面孔，一直偷偷跟在吉星後面，看舉止像是道上的。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收攤的時候，我叫高橋和渡邊跟過去了，先探探對方是什麼底細。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我正好去聯絡一些老夥計。", "name": "？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，你準備出手了？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你忘了？我們當年可是跟鐵齋立過誓的，金盆洗手，換在這條街安度餘生——", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鐵齋現在跟他那個二把手鬥來鬥去，就算他有心幫那個小女生，也未必能抽得開身。", "name": "？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "況且，自家孩子受了委屈，這要是都不出手，我們以後還有臉坐在一起打牌嗎？", "name": "？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_759_1#1$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這倒也是。要怪就怪這十幾年過得太安逸，年輕時的那點衝勁都磨光了……", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別插科打諢了，該辦正事了。", "name": "？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_758_1#1$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g15_higashiroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以——你現在不還是在這裡繼續開店，最後到底是怎麼解決的呢？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，說起來也是奇怪，我當時大包小包收拾好，就準備最後跟鐵齋老爺子道個別，結果臨走的時候，硬是被那幾個黑道堵在了門口……", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g4_kajistreet_dusk", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（深鞠躬）真的——非常抱歉！", "name": "黑道老大&害怕的黑道成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（保持鞠躬）吉星小姐，我們不清楚您和諫崎的松竹會還有往來！實在冒犯了！", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？那個又是什麼？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們已經深刻認識到自己的錯誤了，還請您寬宏大量，放我們一馬！", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些是我們的一點心意，還請吉星大人收下！", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（更深地鞠躬）真的——非常抱歉！", "name": "黑道老大"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g15_higashiroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我最後不僅沒有賠一分錢，還倒賺了不少鑑定珠寶的錢……哼哼，很厲害吧？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "的確是一段跌宕起伏的故事啊……你要是想知道是誰幫你擺平的，我可以幫你打聽打聽？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用啦不用啦，這種事情搞得那麼清楚做什麼嘛～", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幫我的好心人一直沒有出現，說明他就是不想露面啊。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#4$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，說不定真的是因為我運氣比較好——你看，剛才在神社求的籤，“大吉”欸！", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#13$1"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼——你心態這麼好，倒是也沒什麼問題。", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#13$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要日子還能過得下去，怎麼過不是過呢。我現在就想著，要是能在這開一輩子店，那該有多好啊！", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，我看著你也只有羡慕的份，我可沒有家人留下的巨額遺產……", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#3$1"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰說我有一大筆遺產了？", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#6$1"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奶奶一直和我說的是“人生苦短，及時行樂”。每次她賺到錢以後，都帶著我去各種地方旅遊了。", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼想想，好像每次我們回來的時候，都是連飯都吃不起……", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（擦汗）唉，我現在知道你的個性是繼承誰的了，還好你們當初沒有退掉這個店面……", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#4$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個店面怎麼可能退掉嘛，這裡是我們唯一的家，真退掉了就沒地方住啦！這點我還是很清楚的！", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#1$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_windchime_JP", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1897_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來客人了、來客人了。小鋼珠機都開著，投幣就能玩。飲料和零食都到櫃台自取——", "name": "吉星"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1897_1#11$1"}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}